Breath Weapon			KEY:Ambush Drake ~ Breath Weapon	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Race Trait.Ambush Drake Race Trait.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DESC:30-foot cone, once every 1d4 rounds, slow (duration 7 rounds),Will DC 17 negates. Ambush drakes are immune to the breath weapons of other ambush drakes. The save DC is Constitution-based.																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.8
